        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Small Business Tax Fairness Act</strong></p> <p>This bill revises the tax deduction for qualified business income to limit eligibility for such deduction to individual taxpayers. It also modifies rules for calculating the amount of such deduction and limitations on it.</p>]]>
